{"tid":1625770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望各位手足好好諗下裝修既原意","createTime":"2019-10-05T08:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T08:20:43.000Z","uid":159697,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"75405482fa2e89ac924bfef527a7056eef2f6531","tid":1625770,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"我好支持裝修<br />\n但希望手足可以冷靜啲 理智啲諗下<br />\n<br />\n你地搞美心 優品呢啲 全部係抵死 冇問題<br />\n因為呢啲全部解釋到 文宣都幫大家拆左好耐<br />\n令到其他人明白個原意 <br />\n美心係撐黑警 打壓示威者<br />\n優品係福建幫 出黎斬手足<br />\n<br />\n但係唔好令到裝修件事冇左原意<br />\n好似變到咩都搞 <br />\n<br />\n一芳老闆解釋左無限次 人地係特許經營<br />\n搞到自己人只會打擊到我地呢邊陣營<br />\n<br />\n仲有vans 先唔講人地一早講明唔接受敏感題材<br />\n呢個係美國品牌 你踩到美國商家佬條底線<br />\n個邊啲輿論一起 咩人權法 國際民意 唔洗諗<br />\n<br />\n大家一定要冷靜 我地首要對準政權 其次黑警<br />\n商店可以繼續<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">罷食罷買</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住裝修既原意</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"939338ea080d0a6ac6a4d3ce9c295f56ef7313fe","tid":1625770,"uid":225737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"小心被帶風向！唔好理解錯法官唔頒禁制令原因<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eioGmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eioGmS</a>"},{"pid":"c7cd024af5c5eb3e8baea35b8433cd4b5cd20262","tid":1625770,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:17:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b53825814b2d1cf34ad52c25b9755baaee899331","tid":1625770,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:17:52.000Z","msg":"手足諗清楚"},{"pid":"5272e6ca89dcd80711b00fc6dba5c53fdad92e4e","tid":1625770,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"我地要贏！"},{"pid":"4e334786c31770b5ae6fd30962f62590b393228d","tid":1625770,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re